{
  "stem": "19969.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I got there and reported in, I was told that the 7th Army Headquarters was being disbanded, that the 3rd Army was taking over.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The 7th Army was going to be reconstituted in Austria, going to be occupation troops in Austria, and that I would report to General Patton at 3rd Army Headquarters in Augsburg.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Augsburg is quite a large city not far from Munich.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I found the 7th Army Headquarters that evening in a very large building that looked like a municipal building and reported in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they said, well, General Patton's not here, come back in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I found quarters for me and my me that night and the next morning about nine o'clock, I went back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was told by the chief of staff that General Patton who was out and would not be back till sometime after lunch. he said, you go have lunch and you come back at one o'clock.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I came back at one o'clock and I waited a little while and somebody came out and said, OK, General Patton will see you now.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went into one of the room-- a room that he had, a small room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It had a couple of chairs and a desk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saluted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, well, sit down, colonel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, well, he said, colonel, he said-- I am very-- I have some very serious charges against you and some of your men.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, I said, general, I'd like a chance to explain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know what the charges are, but I'd like to have a chance to explain.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, didn't you serve under me in Africa and Sicily?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, yes, I did, general.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
